		{
			dependencies: ["307B3D1F044D7B30"]
			description: [
				"&dEV&r is the age of processing lines. Be prepared to make a LOT of LCRs."
				"While it may seem daunting right now, when you hit &9IV&r you will be able to upgrade all of your"
				"processing lines, without having to make many more."
				""
				"To help accomadate all of the logistics needed to create all of your processing lines, you now have access to &3AE2&r. I suggest setting up your AE2 system first thing."
