		{
			description: [
				"Since there are numerous processing lines in this chapter, you have access to stronger machines designed to make the process a LOT faster. They can also help with ore processing."
				""
				"You have large multiblocks for the following machines:"
				""
				"&6Centrifuge&r"
				"&9Electrolyzer&r"
				"&4Macerator&r"
				""
				"These multiblocks aren't quite as strong as the &9IV+&r ones, but they are much much stronger than singleblocks."
				""
				"They can batch recipes (process ALL of an input at once), and have &l&eperfect overclocking&r. They are similar to multis found in &1Star Technology&r. That being said, they can also only have one energy hatch, and only &8normal maintenance&r hatches."
			]
